model.name: Fribourg2014 - Model of influenza A virus infection dynamics of viral antagonism and innate immune response.

body.pre: This is an ordinary differential equation mathematical model investigating the early responses of human monocyte-derived dendritic cells to infection by two H1N1 influenza A viruses of different clinical outcomes: pandemic A/California/4/2009 and seasonal A/New Caledonia/20/1999.
